snippet.title: Lolita of Labyrinth XBLIG Gameplay
snippet.description:
Lolita of Labyrinth XBLIG Gameplay

"This is a side-scrolling action game. This game has 12 Levels.You must find the key which can open the door to exit. You can stamp monstors, get your coins.If 100 coin is collected, it is exchangeable for a treasure box. If it clears once, difficult stage composition can be played. It created by action game maker."

Created by: aorz

Price: 240 MSP

Download link: http://marketplace.xbox.com/en-US/Product/Lolita-of-Labyrinth/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d802585509f1?DownloadType=GameDemo#LiveZone
